text: Min A-yeong (born 28 January 1975) is a South Korean gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Korea Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Gymnasts at the 1990 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 1990 Asian Games
